  <h1>Privacy Policy – Tradesman's Calc Pro</h1>
  <p class="updated">Last updated: June 6, 2026</p>

  <p>
    Tradesman's Calc Pro ("the App", "we", "us", or "our") is a mobile application
    developed for tradespeople and construction professionals. This Privacy Policy explains
    what information we collect, how we use it, and your rights regarding that information.
  </p>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>
    <strong>We do not collect, store, or transmit any personally identifiable information.</strong>
    The App functions entirely on your device. No account registration is required to use the App.
  </p>
  <p>The only data stored by the App is:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Purchase records</strong> — which in-app modules you have unlocked, stored locally
        on your device using your device's standard storage. This data never leaves your device.</li>
    <li><strong>User preferences</strong> — settings such as unit preferences, stored locally
        on your device.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>2. In-App Purchases</h2>
  <p>
    The App offers optional one-time in-app purchases to unlock individual calculator modules
    or a bundle of all modules. All purchase transactions are processed entirely by Apple
    (App Store) or Google (Google Play) through their respective payment systems. We do not
    receive, process, or store your payment information. Please refer to Apple's or Google's
    privacy policies for information on how they handle your payment and billing data.
  </p>

  <h2>3. Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>
    The App uses the following platform services:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Apple App Store / Google Play Billing</strong> — for processing in-app purchases.
        These services are governed by Apple's and Google's respective privacy policies.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    We do not integrate any third-party analytics, advertising, crash reporting, or tracking SDKs.
  </p>

  <h2>4. Data Sharing</h2>
  <p>
    We do not sell, trade, rent, or share any user data with third parties. Because we do not
    collect personal information, there is no personal data for us to share.
  </p>

  <h2>5. Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>
    The App is intended for use by adults and working professionals. We do not knowingly collect
    any information from children under the age of 13. If you believe a child has provided
    personal information through the App, please contact us so we can address it.
  </p>

  <h2>6. Data Security</h2>
  <p>
    Since all data is stored locally on your device and we collect no personal information,
    the security of your data is governed by your device's own security features (passcode,
    biometric lock, encryption). We recommend keeping your device's operating system up to date.
  </p>

  <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
  <p>
    Since we do not collect or store personal data on our servers, there is no personal data
    for us to access, correct, export, or delete on your behalf. All locally stored data
    (purchase records and preferences) can be cleared by uninstalling the App from your device.
  </p>

  <h2>8. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
  <p>
    We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this
    page with an updated date. We encourage you to review this policy periodically. Continued
    use of the App after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.
  </p>

  <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
  <p>
    If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:<br />
    <a href="mailto:ironshellstudios@gmail.com">ironshellstudios@gmail.com</a>
  </p>

